  92:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c **** /* The definition of messages that can be sent and received on the timer queue.
  93:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c ****  * Two types of message can be queued - messages that manipulate a software timer,
  94:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c ****  * and messages that request the execution of a non-timer related callback.  The
  95:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c ****  * two message types are defined in two separate structures, xTimerParametersType
  96:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c ****  * and xCallbackParametersType respectively. */
