 131:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c **** /* The list in which active timers are stored.  Timers are referenced in expire
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccIlBc3y.s 			page 4


 132:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c ****  * time order, with the nearest expiry time at the front of the list.  Only the
 133:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c ****  * timer service task is allowed to access these lists.
 134:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c ****  * xActiveTimerList1 and xActiveTimerList2 could be at function scope but that
 135:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c ****  * breaks some kernel aware debuggers, and debuggers that reply on removing the
 136:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/timers.c ****  * static qualifier. */
